<ttl id="1002B_S000S_72VQC_T005J" variety="T005J">
<name>OIL PUMP</name>
<para id="RM0000026WD000X" category="A" type-id="30014" name-id="AX138-01" from="200601">
<name>INSTALLATION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000026WD000X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000026WD000X_01_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___00000RJ00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL OIL PUMP ASSEMBLY
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the oil pump to the transaxle case with the 7 bolts.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D003569E03" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>22</t-value1>
<t-value2>225</t-value2>
<t-value4>16</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the O-ring of the oil pump with ATF.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D003629E04" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Confirm the input shaft rotates smoothly with the manual operation after installing the oil pump.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
